建筑师的山姆·卡特（Sam Carter）最初想要吉他手亚当·克里斯蒂安森https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-sam-carter-originally-want--guitarist-guitarist--adam-christianson----- band-tollowlollowing-2024-transphobic-transphobic-conthopic-controversy-3845498?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = Architects-sam-carter-originally-werted-guitarist-adam-adam-adam-christianson-of band-the-band-the-the-the-the-the-the-the-the-2024-2024-transphobic-transphobic-controversySurej Singh Wed, 12 Mar 2025 02:56:32 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3845498 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我一团糟。我在想：“他必须走””</p><p>邮政建筑师的山姆·卡特（Sam Carter）最初是在2024年的跨性别争议之后首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-sam-carter-originally-wanted-guitarist-adam-christianson-out-of-the-band-following-2024-transphobic-controversy-3845498">的吉他手亚当·克里斯蒂安森（Adam Christianson）之后的乐队</a>。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/architects-sam-adam@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/architects">建筑师的</a>主持人山姆·卡特（Sam Carter）透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-speak-out-on-bands-political-views-after-controversial-post-shared-by-guitarist-adam-christianson-3576866">在去年年初，后者的跨性别和同性恋争议</a>之后，他最初希望吉他手亚当·克里斯蒂安森（Adam Christianson）退出乐队。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-interview-whiplash-new-album-the-sky-the-earth-all-between-linkin-park-sleep-token-jordan-fish-3814138">新专辑《天空》，《地球与全部》中的建筑师”：“如果我们现在不打算发挥自己的潜力，我们什么时候？”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 2024年1月，克里斯蒂安森（Christianson）<a href="https://x.com/Timcast/status/1747757208308158719" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在政治评论员蒂姆·普尔（Tim Pool）最初在X（以前为Twitter）上重新发布了X（以前是Twitter）的视频</a><a href="https://twitter.com/SStricklandMMA/status/1747734279516250446" target="_blank" rel="noopener">后</a>，引起了粉丝和乐队成员的愤怒。</p><p>在有争议的视频中，斯特里克兰谈到了过去的一篇文章，他说：“如果我有一个同性恋儿子，我会认为我是一个人，无法成为一个造成如此弱点的人。”他还谈到了过去的反交易帖子，并补充说：“十年前，跨性别是一种精神上的疾病。现在，突然之间，像您这样的人在世界上他妈的weake之以鼻。你是一种感染。您是弱点的定义。世界上所有错误的事情都是因为他妈的你。”</p><p>游泳池随后重新发布了X上的镜头，称斯特里克兰为“他妈的a+伙伴”，并击中了“醒来的感染”。这是克里斯蒂安森（Christianson）在他的饲料上重新提取的信息，但此后已被删除。 </p><figure id="attachment_3828874" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828874" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828874" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="建筑师主唱山姆·卡特（Sam Carter）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_architects_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828874" class="wp-caption-text">建筑师主持人Sam Carter于2024年1月31日在瑞典信贷中心：IWI Onodera/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>音乐家后来道歉，上面写着：“该死！转发是一次完全事故！！除了他妈的特鲁多，我不认可任何人说的话。对不起，大家都慌了！完整的全部瞬间。”</p><p>但是，尽管删除了快速删除和道歉，但演出中的社交媒体和粉丝开始启动Christianson和整个乐队。主唱山姆·卡特（Sam Carter）在接受<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/2025/feb/21/to-say-theres-no-future-is-counterproductive-metal-megastars-architects-on-grief-climate-and-hope-for-humanity" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》（Guardian）</em></a>的讲话时分享说，在第一次了解repost saga时，他最初希望吉他手从乐队中解雇。</p><p> “我一团糟。我在想：他必须走。然后他醒了，我们进行了电话交谈，”卡特解释说。 “他是我的朋友，当我在我身边哭泣时，他把我从地板上捡了起来。他是两个孩子的继父。他是圣人。但是您已经画出了他的这张照片。 [互联网]真是个可怕的地方。”</p><p>鼓手丹·塞尔（Dan Searle）插话，对社交媒体的反应进行了权衡：“他们希望亚当在街上被钉死在街上，没有工作。不仅仅是公然的跨性别行为。”</p><p>几周后，建筑师返回现场舞台，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-speak-out-on-bands-political-views-after-controversial-post-shared-by-guitarist-adam-christianson-3576866">澄清了他们对同性恋恐惧症和恐惧症的立场</a>。卡特在谈到巴黎人群时说：“在这个阶段，没有人判决任何人的性别，种族以及他们爱上的人。我们从来没有。我们永远不会。这不是这个乐队所代表的，也不是该乐队所代表的。我们爱你们每个人。” </p><figure id="attachment_3426767" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3426767" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3426767" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns.jpg" alt="建筑师的山姆·卡特。学分：Mariano Regidor通过Redferns" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Sam-Carter-of-Architects.-Credit-Mariano-Regidor-via-Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3426767" class="wp-caption-text">建筑师的山姆·卡特。学分：Mariano Regidor通过Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>在其他新闻中，建筑师最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-announce-2025-uk-and-european-tour-including-huge-london-show-buy-tickets-3845013">宣布了2025年的英国和欧洲头条新闻之旅</a>。 Brighton Metalcore乐队将于今年秋天在上个月发行的第11张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/architects-interview-whiplash-new-album-the-sky-the-earth-all-between-linkin-park-sleep-token-jordan-fish-3814138">《 Sky，The Earth＆Whoot Mooke》的第11张专辑“ The Sky，The Earth＆All Mooken”</a> （由前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Bring Me Horizo​​n</a>成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jordan-fish">Jordan Fish</a>制作）。</p><p>门票将于本周五（3月14日）在GMT/GMT上午10点进行通用销售 - <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Farchitects-tickets%2Fartist%2F1615917" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里</a>（英国）和<a href="https://www.architectsofficial.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>